         <abstract id="aspace_955f8d7200d9274111a404ac662b3e9b">The original accession consists of original and typed copies of letters sent home by American servicemen from various training camps in the United States and from overseas campaigns during World War II, many of which Mina Curtiss used for her 1944 book, <title render="italic">
